rovides contract development and manufacturing services to a range of multinational corporations and specialty companies. It exports its products. The company was formerly known as Glenmark Life Sciences Limited and changed its name to Alivus Life Sciences Limited in December 2024. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Mumbai, India. Alivus Life Sciences Limited is a subsidiary of Nirma Limited."}}